Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.tables

Class TableServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>>

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.service.tables.TableServiceFluent<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of UiServiceFluent for chaining fluent methods.
public class TableServiceFluent<T extends UiServiceFluent<?>> extends Object
Provides fluent methods for interacting with table components in the UI.

This class offers functionality for reading, inserting, filtering, and sorting table data, as well as validating table contents.
